Votes cast

p1 = qplot( x=year, y=cast, 
            data=precinct.26, 
            color=type, 
            geom=c("point", "line")
            ) + labs(title="Votes Cast By Year and Election Type -- Precinct 26: State College East 3")
ggsave(filename="votes-cast.png", plot=p1)
